      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get what ur saying, but is it really a \"fact\" that it'll be uneven? mcm economists argue that capital investment from top earners actually trickles down and creates jobs for everyone else. arent there legitimate studies that say this kind of supply-side approach is the most effective way to grow the economy in the long run?",
